    <div class="mb--large">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #6B6B6B;">Raise awareness</h3>
      <p>Did you know that the average couple invites 140 guests to their wedding? That’s 140 opportunities to raise the profile of your organization and the important work you do. Your name, logo, website and mission will be featured on our partners’ page and highlighted regularly on our blog and social media. Your organization’s name and website will also appear on the couple's’ wedding registry webpage.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb--large">
      <h3 style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #6B6B6B;">Get funded</h3>
      <p>Heartful.ly is an elegant, personalized fundraising platform that supports the important work your organization is doing. We will collaborate with your organization to develop a narrative and itemized gift list to package your work into wedding registries. After that, we take care of everything including safely and securely processing donations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb--large">
      <h3 style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #6B6B6B;">Build relationships</h3>
      <p>By asking guests to contribute to such a meaningful wedding present, we believe your mission will resonate beyond the couple’s wedding day and will result in new friends, advocates and supporters of your organization and cause.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

